OL,3,CGrieving husband says family
OL,4,C'sentenced for life' as wife killed by
OL,5,Cdrunk driver
OL,7,FThe husband of a mother of three from
OL,8,FBracknell who died in a drink-driving
OL,9,Fcollision says his family has been
OL,10,Fdealt a life sentence following the
OL,11,Fcrash.
OL,13,FBenedicta Owusu Buabeng was hit by a
OL,14,Fman who was 1.5 times over the drink-
OL,15,Fdriving limit after he left a
OL,16,FChristmas Party in December 2022.
OL,18,FSolomon Amissah was jailed for 11
OL,19,Fyears after pleading guilty to death
OL,20,Fby dangerous driving.
