OL,7,FThames Valley Police says arrests for
OL,8,Fthis conviction have increased by 7.5%
OL,9,Fin the past year.
OL,11,FBenedicta's husband, Nana Kofi, says
OL,12,Fit has been difficult for him to even
OL,13,Fbegin grieving as he has continued
OL,14,Fworking and caring for his three
OL,15,Fchildren.
OL,17,FNana hopes by speaking out about the
OL,18,Fimpact of drink-driving - he can
OL,19,Fencourage others to think twice before
OL,20,Fdoing the same.
