OL,7,F"It's always tough when the kids are
OL,8,Ftrying to settle in life and piece
OL,9,Ftogether what happened to their mum.
OL,11,F"To those who would drink and drive,
OL,12,For even those who would drive
OL,13,Fcarelessly, they may get 7`10 years,
OL,14,Fbut they are also sentencing the
OL,15,Ffamily of the person who will be
