OL,7,FThames Valley Police is urging anyone
OL,8,Fthinking of driving after having a
OL,9,Fdrink during the Euros to plan ahead
OL,10,Fand not take the risk, so no more
OL,11,Ffamilies are left without loved ones
OL,12,Fthis Summer.
OL,14,FDet Con Joy Jarvis, Thames Valley
OL,15,FPolice Serious Collision Unit said:
OL,16,F"It's summer at the moment, so there
OL,17,Fare lots of summer events going on,
OL,18,FBBQs, weddings, the Euros.
