OL,7,F"I would say to drivers, before they
OL,8,Fget in a car, just make a plan. If
OL,9,Fyou're going to drink, arrange a taxi,
OL,10,Fhave a designated driver.
OL,12,F"Don't just have those one or two
OL,13,Fdrinks and get into a car thinking
OL,14,Fyou'll be ok, you won't be ok."
